channel.title: Lol, anyone else seen this?
channel.description:
Looky here:
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2cyr1fm.jpg[/img]
Notice his xp. As we all know, the maximum integer in java is 2147483647. So what happens when he gains ~100m more xp? Runescape's gonna have a bit of a problem on there hands. Although they could easily convert the int to a long but idc, I still would like to see what happens.
